  {-V|--version}
  {--repair}")

  (define cache-metadata-size-help
          "Usage: cache_metadata_size [options]
Options:
  {-h|--help}
  {-V|--version}
  {--block-size <sectors>}
  {--device-size <sectors>}
  {--nr-blocks <natural>}
  {--max-hint-width <nr bytes>}

These all relate to the size of the fast device (eg, SSD), rather
